Job Description
Responsible for maintaining websites. Ensure sites are functioning properly and are available to users. Tests speed of access and improves upon loading speed.
Generate and revise web
and analyze site traffic.
Serve as the server
and manage access rights of different users on website
Skills
Need a good working knowledge of HTML, and experience of writing web pages in a combination of codes.
•Dreamweaver
•Photoshop
•Flash and Fireworks
•CSS
•Javascript
•.Net
